// Body: lib/comp170.tpa (design docs/design/chapters/01-prologue.md).

BEGIN @170 DESIGNATED 170 GROUP @1001 LABEL ~csr_jailbreak~
REQUIRE_PREDICATE (FILE_EXISTS_IN_GAME ~bd0120.are~) @9000
REQUIRE_COMPONENT ~chriz-sod-remix/setup-chriz-sod-remix.tp2~ ~140~ ~Component 170 (the Korlasz jailbreak) requires component 140 (skip the Korlasz dungeon).~

INCLUDE ~chriz-sod-remix/lib/comp170.tpa~

