// ============================================================
// 220 — the dwarven dig site re-garrisoned
// ============================================================
// BD1100/BD1200's ~200 pre-placed hostiles become a handful of
// purposeful fights (dwarf barricade, horde room, honor guard at
// the sealed door); shadowed souls / bone bats / the Unsleeping
// Guardian are hard-banned; 80% of the cut kill-XP returns as one
// chunk on the lich clean-kill. Quest wiring (Semahl's five
// attackers, Deepvein's wight, Coldhearth machinery) preserved by
// construction. docs/design/chapters/02-coastway.md §3.

BEGIN @220 DESIGNATED 220 GROUP @1002 LABEL ~csr_digsite~
REQUIRE_PREDICATE (FILE_EXISTS_IN_GAME ~bd1100.are~) @9000
REQUIRE_PREDICATE (FILE_EXISTS_IN_GAME ~bd1200.are~) @9000

INCLUDE ~chriz-sod-remix/lib/comp220.tpa~

