// named TranBD7220) are re-targeted at each other, so the wyrm
// cave's deep passage opens straight into the temple and back.
// Region names stay, so every vanilla EscapeAreaObject keeps
// working — the temple's fleeing cultist now runs into the
// dragon cave. Plus BD7200 overland cuts (28) and the six
